## 🔧 Migration Paths

### From v4.0.x to v4.1.0

```bash
# Automatic migration
./payload/install.sh --upgrade

# Manual verification
/version 4.1.0 --dry-run
```

**Changes Required:**
- Update installer references from `installer/` to `payload/`
- Verify Claude output styles integration
- Test enhanced template processing

### From v3.x to v4.1.0

```bash
# Backup existing installation
cp -r .apm .apm.backup

# Fresh installation recommended
./payload/install.sh --fresh

# Migrate custom configurations
/migrate-from-v3 --source=.apm.backup
```

**Major Changes:**
- Complete architecture overhaul
- New native sub-agent system
- Enhanced performance and reliability

